lead_paragraph: Anders Jacobsen of Norway defeated the four-time Olympic champion Simon Ammann of Switzerland to win the second ski jumping World Cup of the Four Hills tour in Garmisch-Partenkirchen, Germany.

headline.main: Norwegian Beats Gold Medalist in Ski Jumping
